defaultWest Midlands
default, WS Atkins, April 2012, provides at,
default paragraph 6.4.8, that 30% of trips are business trips.  We have from note 1 above 98,800 generated trips.  Hence there are likely to be 98,800 x 0.3 = 29,640 
defaultgenerateddefault business trips.  
